{"tid":984484,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西行程請教","createTime":"2019-01-16T23:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T18:41:32.000Z","uid":231598,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5de52824cc53472bdfd336a9aab8603c89c77536","tid":984484,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T23:58:40.000Z","msg":"打算去半年旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（東南亞、南美、埃及、東西歐、俄羅斯）<br />\n<br />\n今年二月尾首先飛<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">巴西</span>聖保羅，<br />\n其實主要想去睇巴西嘉年華，<br />\n但因為飛里約機票太貴，又有幾日時間淨，<br />\n所以就飛聖保羅（單程~<span style=\"color: red;\">3800</span>HKD）。<br />\n<br />\n上網睇去巴西多數啲人都係去<br />\n1. 里約（睇基督像、麵包山、沙灘等）<br />\n2. 聖保羅（都好似冇咩睇<br />\n3. 巴西利亞（睇建築）<br />\n4. 伊瓜蘇瀑布<br />\n5. 亞馬遜熱帶雨林<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想各位巴絲俾少少意見<br />\n1. 係咪巴西主要都係玩以上嘅野？<br />\n2. 巴西嘉年華嘅賣飛情況<br />\n3. 巴西有咩景點、美食值得推介？"},{"pid":"f0b46e78711e1d701c309742d6a25dfc33600adc","tid":984484,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:05:08.000Z","msg":"半年旅行 一定好撚嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1d8b79833c594e319f51404ef818fc0ab4d26d","tid":984484,"uid":231598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f0b46e78711e1d701c309742d6a25dfc33600adc","tid":984484,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:05:08.000Z","msg":"半年旅行 一定好撚嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:07:47.000Z","msg":"出黎做左野幾年，儲左啲錢<br />\n當出去見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09209a9a5aadb9eb34700f674cf892651badbbe","tid":984484,"uid":155601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5de52824cc53472bdfd336a9aab8603c89c77536","tid":984484,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T23:58:40.000Z","msg":"打算去半年旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（東南亞、南美、埃及、東